M.G.L. c. 260, \u00a7 2A.proposition: Relevant authorities include, without limitation: Massachusetts statute of limitations for tort actions (M.G.L. c. 260, § 2A), Massachusetts statutes and provisions regulating animals and dogs contained in Massachusetts General Laws chapter 140 (see, e.g., provisions governing dogs and owner responsibility), and governing case law on negligence and duty in Massachusetts.
